<li class='cover' id='bookCover_40856825'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/40856825-martin-dressler"><img alt="Martin Dressler: The Tale of an American Dreamer" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1531850270l/40856825._SX98_.jpg" />
